        "role": "link",
        "name": "Hollywood\u2019s Mirage Earnings Season: Fear That the Worst Isn\u2019t Here Yet"
      },
      {
        "role": "text",
        "name": "Summer blockbusters and streaming hits could obscure the economic pain of entertainment giants facing the rest of the year amid an advertising pullback, inflation drag and\u202fsupply chain issues."
