        "role": "link",
        "name": "Inside \u2018House of the Dragon\u2019 Part 2: \u201cIt\u2019s a Powerful, Dark, Shakespearean Tragedy\u201d"
      },
      {
        "role": "text",
        "name": "The two-part report continues on the set of 'Dragon': The cast opens up about their characters, the showrunners explain how the new series tackles issues of race and sexual violence, and a look at the franchise\u2019s future."
      },
